lastCommit.message:
fix: Cloudflare Pages build configuration

- Fix root package.json build command to delegate to frontend
- Remove wrangler.toml which was causing configuration conflicts
- Clean up build artifacts from frontend/dist/ and frontend/public/data/
- Update .gitignore to properly exclude frontend build artifacts
- Ensure protocol documentation generator handles empty schemas gracefully

Fixes Cloudflare Pages build failures by using correct build command from root
